data.text: @juliaeberry i've hated him ever since a friend of my mother's met him in an official capacity on his first visit to canada with diana. she said he was rude & dismissive to his wife, and basically made fun of her / was irritated that all the crowds wanted to meet her. he's a capital D Douche.
